Package: quickReg
Title: Build Regression Models and Display the Results Using 'ggplot2'
Version: 1.6.0
Authors@R: person("Xikun", "Han", email = "hanxikun2014@163.com",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provide a set of functions to build regression models automatically for 
 multiple exposures (x) and outcomes (y) with or without adjusting for covariates, 
 format the results into a data frame, and visualize model results using 'ggplot2'.
URL: URL: https://github.com/XikunHan/quickReg
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 2.0.0),
    rlang (>= 0.1.2),
    survival,
    psych,
    utils,
    stats,
    nortest,
    dplyr
Suggests:
    ggthemes,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
